commitResults.messageBody:
Implementation of Level 0.
Rename, Greet, Exit.

Level-1: Echo

echos commands entered by the user, and exits when the user types the command bye

Level 2. Add, List

Added the ability to store whatever text entered by the user and display them back to the user when requested.

Implemented
-The ability to mark tasks as done.
-The ability to change the status back to not done.
-Represented Tasks as a class

Added Support for tracking three types of tasks:

ToDos: tasks without any date/time attached to it e.g., visit new theme park

Deadlines: tasks that need to be done before a specific date/time e.g., submit report by 11/10/2019 5pm

Events: tasks that start at a specific date/time and ends at a specific date/time
e.g., (a) team project meeting 2/10/2019 2-4pm (b) orientation week 4/10/2019 to 11/10/2019
